Profile Manipulation
The following is a section of resources related to creating/manipulating unity profiles
--

Gets a profile from its identifier
GET /projects/{proj_name}/{proj_version}/profiles/{profile_id}
< 200
< Content-Type: application/json
{
    "owner": "user@domain.com",
    "overlay":
    [
        "a": { type: "Integer", value: 1 },
        "b": { type: "String", value : "2"},
        "c": { type: "Color", values : { r: 128, g: 128, b: 128 } }
    ],
    "description" : "Changed a setting to be something different"
}

Gets a profile from its identifier
PUT /projects/{proj_name}/{proj_version}/profiles/{profile_id}
> Accept: application/json
> Content-Type: application/json
{
    "owner": "user@domain.com",
    "overlay":
    [
        "a": { type: "Integer", value: 1 },
        "b": { type: "String", value : "2"},
        "c": { type: "Color", values : { r: 128, g: 128, b: 128 }
    ],
    "description" : "Changed a setting to be something different"
}
< 201




